text: Looks like a betting tech company that have now launched their own bookmaker (yesterday). The odds on their twitter stream were fairly good, i.e. better than other bookmakers and for one pick better than BSP, but generally their greyhound odds look pretty pedestrian. Legal structure is a tad unclear. One legal company trading as another, neither of which is the recently incorporated Bresbet Ltd entity. Funds are not protected, and the stated requirements for withdrawals may prove onerous for some. However, site is clean and works well, so let's hope their odds improve and their service is as good as their presentation.
